{'BugID': 'WICKET-4997', 'Summary': 'Mounted bookmarkable Page not recreated on Session Expiry', 'Description': "With the default true of org.apache.wicket.settings.IPageSettings#getRecreateMountedPagesAfterExpiry() PageExpiryException is thrown when a Link on a page is clicked.

